title: Mediterranean Deli
typeOfFood: Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Catering, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Large selection of deli food as well a menu. Sells fresh pita bread. A lot of meatstuff, but the deli dishes, sold by weight, are labeled if "vegan," "vegetarian," "gluten-free," or "nut-free." The desserts, however, might contain honey or sugar syrup (indicated). Order at the counter, and food is delivered to your table. Street parking only.
